[Infection with _Yersinia pestis_ is endemic in this area of central
Africa. ProMED has posted outbreaks or suspected outbreaks in Uganda
and the Democratic Republic of the Congo previously, as listed below.
As stated in the report, the laboratory confirmation of the infection
is so far lacking. - Mod.LL]
